race.comment: DIAMANTINA ROSE (4) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in all four career outings to date and strikes a very winnable contest here. Yoshida has been in the irons for all four starts so far and sticks today. Rates the testing material against this lot. HASANA (5) resumes but showed glimpses of ability in her first preparation and has tuned up for this with a recent trial. Looms as the main danger. BOLD LOUIE (1) is facing the starter for the first time but wasn't too far away in a recent trial and any market support must be noted. I'LLTELLYOUAFTER (9) looks to be improving with racing and gets in light with the claim. In the mix. CASUAL MAN (2) will be at peak fitness now and may earn some minor money.
